parameters.text:
=Analyze this email and classify its priority.

From: {{ $json.from }}
Subject: {{ $json.subject }}
Body: {{ $json.text || $json.snippet }}

Classify whether this email:
- is_priority: true if it is urgent, high-priority, time-sensitive, or contains action items; false otherwise
- priority_type: one of "urgent", "action_required", "important", or "none"
- summary: a single sentence describing what this email is about
- action_items: array of specific actions the recipient needs to take (empty array if none)

=🚨 *Priority Email Alert*

*From:* {{ $("Gmail - New Unread Emails").item.json.from }}
*Subject:* {{ $("Gmail - New Unread Emails").item.json.subject }}
*Type:* {{ $json.priority_type.toUpperCase() }}

📋 *Summary:* {{ $json.summary }}

✅ *Action Items:*
{{ $json.action_items.map((item, i) => (i+1) + ". " + item).join("\n") || "None" }}
